##Instructions

Take 3 minutes, try to find the “ugliest” and “most beautifully designed” sites on the internet.

View the index.html page using Glitch web preview. Identify that content appears on the page but that it isn’t styled.

Uncomment the <script> and <link> tags. Then view the refreshed web preview. Inspect the HTML. Predictions what each class is doing.

Read documentation for Bulma.io and how it confirms our understanding of how the elements and classnames are building the hero and columns.

Use the documentation to figure out how to add a card to a column.

Create the third row of columns, and add three cards. Give each card an image and card content that has a song name, and the artists name.

Add a fourth row of cards to the page.

Create a style.css file.
